<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَكَيْفَ تُدْرِكُ شَيْئًا لَمْ تَطْلُبْهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَا هَذَا عَلَيْكَ بِالْجِدِّ وَالاجْتِهَادِ , وَخَلِّ <span class="c4">[هَذَا]</span> الْكَسَلَ وَالرُّقَادَ فَطَرِيقُكَ لا بُدَّ لَهَا مِنْ زَادٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(انْهَضْ إِلَى الْمَعَالِي ... وَأَقْبِلْ وَلا تُبَالِي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(وَخُذْ مِنَ الزَّمَانِ ... حَظًّا فَأَنْتَ فَانِي)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(الْهِمَمُ الْعَلِيَّةْ ... وَالْمُهَجُ الأَبِيَّةْ)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(تُقَرِّبُ الْمَنِيَّةْ ... مِنْكَ أَوِ الأُمْنِيَّةْ)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(الْمَجْدُ بِالْمُخَاطَرَةْ ... وَالنَّصْرُ بِالْمُصَابَرَةْ)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(كَمْ رَاحَةٍ فِي الْعُزْلَةْ ... وَعَمَلٍ فِي الْعُطْلَةْ)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(لَيْسَ يَدُومُ حَالٌ ... شَحْمُ الْمُنَى هُزَالٌ)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(مَا لِلْوَرَى فِي غَفْلَةْ ... قَدْ خُدِعُوا بِالْمُهْلَةْ)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(أَلا لَبِيبٌ يَعْقِلُ ... أَلا جَهُولٌ يَسْأَلُ)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(أَأَنْتُمُ فِي رِيبَةْ ... مَا أَعْظَمُ الْمُصَيِبةْ)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(دُنْيَاكُمُ حَبِيبَةْ ... لِحُسْنِهَا وَالطِّيبَةْ)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(لَكِنَّهَا غَدَّارَةْ ... خَدَّاعَةٌ غَرَّارَةْ)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(لَيْسَ لَهَا حَبِيبُ ... زَوَالُهَا قَرِيبُ)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(كَالْمُومِسِ الْبَغِيِّ ... تَلْبَسُ كُلَّ زِيِّ)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(خَلَوبَةٌ خَوَّانَةْ ... لَيْسَ لَهَا أَمَانَةْ)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(عَزِيزُهَا ذَلِيلُ ... كَثِيرُهَا قَلِيلُ)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(تُفَرِّقُ الأَحْبَابَا ... تُشَتِّتُ الأَتْرَابَا)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">(حَرْبٌ لِمَنْ سَالَمَهَا ... تَمَلُّ مَنْ لازَمَهَا)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c2">(لِقَاؤُهَا فِرَاقُ ... وَعُرْسُهَا طَلاقُ)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c2">(وِصَالُهَا صدود ... ووعدها وعيد)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c2">(وصالها عنا ... صدودها بلا)</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c2">(عُقُودُهَا مَنْقُوضَةْ ... عُهُودُهَا مَرْفُوضَةْ)</span><a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c2">(شَرَابُهَا سَرَابُ ... نَعِيمُهَا عذاب)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>